&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working with the Legal Counsel, the Paralegal will be a crucial team member of the legal team, assisting with corporate, immigration and employment law matters. The Paralegal will work with the Legal Counsel to manage ChainSafe’s day-to-day and strategic legal needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Will Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
